    Class
    A Class is akin to an abstract base Class but is constrained to the definition of member variables.

    A ClassAttribute expresses a three-way relationship between a Class.id, an Attribute.id and an AttributeType.id.

    A ClassAttributePK defines the primary key for an instance of ClassAttribute.
    EntityAttributeValue
    An EntityAttributeValue is the reification of a ClassAttribute plus a value.
